Robert Van Wyk‎Rahway High School Musical Theater (cast, pit, crew)
May 5 at 7:32 PM ·

Today, Donors Choose, generous supporters gave a great assist to Rahway music students.

We are down to our last project. One iPad down, One left to go! Matching money still in the table. Great day providing resources for our Rahway kids.

My students will OVERCOME and make me jump 4 joy! In this crisis, access to technology has proven critical Technology=great equalizer! Today only every $ is matched!. 23years changing lives through the arts in a diverse school in NJ! #musicmatters

Rahway Students,

Thinking of you all and hope you are safe and healthy. Please continue to do your assignments as the future awaits you all. We need to keep up with our work.

In the meantime let us keep our spirits up!

Please help me celebrate #FancyFriday.

Let's wake up, and dress up tomorrow in our fanciest clothes, makeup, hair, whatever you are feeling. Tweet a picture out to Rahway does Fancy Friday at #FancyFriday on Twitter or Facebook.

Keep up your good work!
